[center][color=#8e7cc3][size=6][size=5]WellGram FuGirl Teeth 1.0 [/size]
[/size][/color][color=#8e7cc3]by[/color] [url=http://wellgramskyrim.tumblr.com/]Aydoo/WellGramarye[/url]

[color=#8e7cc3][size=3]

[img]https://41.media.tumblr.com/c87da9aaf9ebe24daf3b404773aff6b0/tumblr_nvnuztTa8F1u3zq8lo2_r1_1280.jpg[/img]

Chompers designed in the style of "Denki-gai no Honya-san's" Fu Girl.
This is a replacer texture best used with custom races unless you want everyone else to have chompers too.

This is a Fu Girl:

[/size][/color][img]https://41.media.tumblr.com/bbd74aac5e7f3dde90e8b3b151c33b06/tumblr_nvnuztTa8F1u3zq8lo1_250.png[/img]
[size=4]
[color=#8e7cc3][size=6]GO FORTH AND CHOMP!
Make sure to take plenty of shots of those cute smiles![/size][/color]

[img]http://i.imgur.com/60OOu0S.gif[/img]

[size=5]Installation:[/size][/size][color=#8e7cc3][size=3]
Install in your Race's Mouth/Â  Folder, rename as needed.

For example my follower's path is:
data/textures/actors/character/Gramarye/Mouth/
